pment Report Unit (HDRU), UNDP Asia\u2010Pacific Regional Centre, Colombo office, conducted the East Asia stakeholder consultation during April 2010 as part of its ongoing work on APHDR on Climate Change. The objectives of the stakeholder consultations were two\u2010fold: to be informed by views, experiences and priorities of countries in the region, while strengthening cross\u2010country networks, and to obtain buy\u2010in for the RHDR from stakeholders. 22 participants from different type of organizations participated in the consultation. Figure 1 shows the participation of different organization in the consultation.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "765ea214-3854-492c-947f-50352dd92441": {"__data__": {"id_": "765ea214-3854-492c-947f-50352dd92441", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-climate-change-asia-stakeholders-consultation-report", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific Human Development Report on Climate Change: Asia Stakeholders Consultation Report", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-climate-change-asia-stakeholders-consultation-report", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "297b43d61c24171a57c03cdc3f39c40dcd8c00f9c7f39920730789577f2f9b19"}, "2": {"node_id": "dccd89db-7d13-465b-923d-e77cb06ada3b", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-climat